**LIX readability score calculator:** https://www.skolverket.se/undervisning/stod-i-undervisningen/laromrade-och-amnen-i-grundskolan/utveckling-av-sprak-och-kommunikation/larresurser-och-stodmaterial/lasbarhetsindex-lix

**Number of words:** 100

**Number of long words (more than 6 letters):** 30

**Number of sentences:** 8

**LIX formula:** LIX = 36.29 + (0.043 * (words / sentences)) + (0.244 * (long words / words))

**LIX score:** LIX = 36.29 + (0.043 * (100 / 8)) + (0.244 * (30 / 100)) = **36.33**

**Result:** LIX=36.33